author: AFP
title: Global virus deaths pass 1,50,000 as Donald Trump endorses lockdown protests
description: Coronavirus deaths have surged past 150,000 worldwide with nearly a quarter of them in the United States, where President Donald Trump lent his support to protestors rallying against lockdown orders.
